    "III-C demands exceptionally high data set quality, whereas some datasets (including NAB, UCR, Yahoo) fail to offer labels without positional bias.",
    "Therefore, the result merely provide a approximate reference on these datasets.",
    "We manually set a relatively suitable latency limit (K) for each dataset based on the sampling frequency and label quality of the dataset to evaluate the performance of each method under strict real-time requirements.",
    "The over- all results are shown in Table II.",
    "Compared to the results without delay-constraint, it can be seen that the performance of some methods significantly deteriorates in this setup, even approaching a 50% decrease (e.g., Anomaly Transformer on TODS)."
